Run prepare_build.sh for the automake stuff, then make to compile the isbd2
executable.


Building
========
To specify include and or library directories (e.g. for boost) use the
configure script:
# CPPFLAGS="-I/path/to/boost/include/" LDFLAGS="-L/path/to/boost/lib/" ./configure


Examples
========

# Run isbd2 on tcp port 4723 whith usb2ser adapter on /dev/ttyUSB0 (linux)
# ./isbd2 --port 4723 --device /dev/ttyUSB0

# Run isbd2 on tcp port 4723 on COM1 (windows)
# isbd2.exe --port 4723 --device COM1
